These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, peas, onion, cauliflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, rock, folk, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, colombian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, snake, rabbit
 1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 2. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
 3. the canadian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 4. the colombian is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 5. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 7. the malaysian is the person eating onion##1
 8. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the rabbit and the fan of r&b##2
10. the person eating radish is the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the fan of folk is the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | onion  | radish    | cauliflower    | peas   |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | electronic   | folk       | r&b    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | canadian | egyptian    | colombian |
| Pet           | mouse | rabbit       | cat | snake     |

