.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, garlic, onion, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, cooking, traveling, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, brazilian, argentine, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, handball, cricket, tennis
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
 2. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 4. the person eating garlic is the malaysian##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 6. the malaysian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 7. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 8. the french is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
 9. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating onion is in an odd position##4
11. the argentine is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | kiwi  | garlic    | onion     | plum       |
| Hobby         | traveling | rock-climbing | fishing   | cooking |
| Nationality   | argentine | malaysian   | brazilian   | french    |
| Sport         | cricket | tennis  | skiing | handball   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, fanta, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, videographer, photographer, bartender
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, canadian, japanese, colombian
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, turtle, ferret
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the electrician##3
 2. the canadian is the photographer##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 4. the electrician is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the bartender##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the colombian##1
 8. the bartender is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the mexican##1
10. the owner of the bird is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade | fanta   | cola    | iced-tea      |
| Job           | photographer | electrician | videographer | bartender     |
| Nationality   | canadian      | colombian   | mexican   | japanese |
| Pet           | ferret         | bird       | turtle  | guinea-pig       |

