.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, tea, 7up
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, pear, broccoli, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, gardening, photography, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cricket, badminton, skateboarding
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
12. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up       | tea   | lemonade   | almond-milk   |
| Food       | pear        | radish | nectarine    | broccoli       |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | gardening    | photography  | baking |
| Sport      | cricket  | badminton  | baseball | skateboarding    |

