.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, zucchini, kale, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, writing, collecting, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, chef, writer, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, soccer, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person eating garlic##2
 3. the writer is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the chef is the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the coach is on the left or right of the chef##3
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating zucchini is the coach##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the chef##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
10. the chef is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | kale    | garlic      | eggplant          | zucchini    |
| Hobby   | writing | baking       | collecting | camping |
| Job     | police-officer     | writer      | chef     | coach |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | baseball | soccer        | swimming   |

