.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, almond-milk, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, lime, zucchini, pineapple
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, jazz, electronic, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: french, russian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of punk is between the nigerian and the fan of jazz##2
 7. the fan of electronic is the person eating zucchini##1
 8. the person drinking water is the person eating zucchini##1
 9. the russian is on the far right##1
10. the french is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | water    | fanta       | soy-milk       |
| Food          | pineapple    | zucchini | lime | asparagus     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | electronic        | punk    | jazz   |
| Nationality   | french  | nigerian      | thai    | russian |

