4 different pets are kept: hamster, fish, bird, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, bike, bus
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 2. the argentine is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the indian##3
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 6. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
 9. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
10. the british is on the far right##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
12. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | musical    | adventure  | animation      |
| Nationality   | indian      | turkish | argentine | british   |
