 2. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the goat##2
 3. the thai is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the mexican is on the right of the chinese##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the colombian##1
 9. the owner of the snake is between the thai and the person watching spy movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
12. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

