The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, sports, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, country, metal, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, surfing, tennis
 1. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of trance is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's sport is soccer##2
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
11. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of country is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
13. the fan of metal is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | corn     | watermelon      | artichoke  | pumpkin        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | sports | adventure | action      |
| Music-Genre   | country      | trance        | techno        | metal        |
