There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, american, german, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, soccer, water-polo, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the lawyer is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the spanish##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the german is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
 8. the spanish is on the right of the german##1
 9. the pilot is on the left of the lawyer##1
10. the dressmaker is in an even position##4
11. the indonesian is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | juice      | almond-milk           | milk |
| Job           | pilot | lawyer | teacher | dressmaker        |
| Nationality   | german      | spanish  | indonesian          | american      |
| Sport         | snowboarding       | water-polo    | weightlifting       | soccer       |

