The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, skateboard, bike
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 2. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 4. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
11. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
