 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the pilot##3
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the software-developer##2
 5. the person eating cabbage is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the doctor is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 9. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
11. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
12. the pilot is on the left or right of the doctor##3
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |   3    |     4      |
