 4. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
11. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite       | water | fanta        | cola        |
| Hobby         | gardening | fishing       | sudoku | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | spy        | documentary    | horror      |
| Sport         | baseball     | handball    | tennis | rugby   |

