.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, indie, funk, country
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, canadian, turkish, nigerian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, badminton, skateboarding, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, roller, taxi, quad-bike
 1. the fan of country is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the mexican and the nigerian##2
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the canadian##1
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the fan of indie is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 8. the nigerian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the mexican is in an even position##4
11. the mexican is on the far right##1
12. the fan of jazz is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | jazz | country     | funk        |
| Nationality   | turkish | nigerian  | canadian     | mexican |
| Sport         | badminton    | rowing | skateboarding      | basketball |
| Transport     | quad-bike | roller     | taxi | bus       |

 